      "audioUrl": "audio/drifter_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo01_01.mp3",
      "text": "You like to gamble, right Wraith?",
      "duration": 2.515
    },
    {
      "order": 2,
      "character": "Wraith",
      "audioFile": "wraith_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo01_02",
      "audioUrl": "audio/wraith_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo01_02.mp3",
      "text": "I know where you're going with this: here's the problem with gambling on body counts with you.  You're a psychotic killing machine, which means if I incentivize you to kill more on top of that, there's a non zero chance that you don\u2019t finish the ritual because you want to pad your numbers.",
      "duration": 13.049
    },
    {
      "order": 3,
      "character": "Drifter",
      "audioFile": "drifter_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo01_03",
      "audioUrl": "audio/drifter_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo01_03.mp3",
      "text": "You really thought this through.",
      "duration": 2.138
    },
    {
      "order": 4,
      "character": "Wraith",
      "audioFile": "wraith_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo01_04",
      "audioUrl": "audio/wraith_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo01_04.mp3",
      "text": "I really wanted to make it work",
      "duration": 1.913
    },
    {
      "order": 5,
      "character": "Drifter",
      "audioFile": "drifter_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo01_05",
      "audioUrl": "audio/drifter_match_start_drifter_wraith_convo01_05.mp3",
      "text": "Thanks for considering it.",
      "duration": 2.204
    }
  ]
